{
  "description": "A vibrant fireworks display illuminates the night sky above a cityscape and a bridge spanning a body of water. The fireworks are predominantly golden and white with streaks of red and blue, bursting outwards in a radial pattern. Below, a long, illuminated bridge with a distinctive architectural design extends across the dark water. The cityscape in the background is a mix of skyscrapers and buildings with visible lights, indicating an urban environment. The water is dark and reflects some of the city lights and the fireworks. The overall scene evokes a sense of celebration and grandeur.",
